<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>AI on ifindv's Blog</title><link>https://ifindv.github.io/categories/ai/</link><description>Recent content in AI on ifindv's Blog</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-cn</language><copyright>© 2026 ifindv</copyright><lastBuildDate>Fri, 01 May 2026 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://ifindv.github.io/categories/ai/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>claude code 教程：CLI</title><link>https://ifindv.github.io/posts/claude-code-10-cli/</link><pubDate>Fri, 01 May 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://ifindv.github.io/posts/claude-code-10-cli/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;Claude Code命令行界面（CLI）提供了强大的命令行工具，用于自动化、CI/CD集成和高级工作流程。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>claude code 教程：advanced</title><link>https://ifindv.github.io/posts/claude-code-09-advanced/</link><pubDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://ifindv.github.io/posts/claude-code-09-advanced/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;高级功能扩展了Claude Code的核心能力，包括规划、推理、自动化和控制机制。这些功能为复杂的开发任务、代码审查、自动化和多会话管理提供了复杂的工作流程。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>claude code 教程：checkpoints</title><link>https://ifindv.github.io/posts/claude-code-08-checkpoints/</link><pubDate>Wed, 29 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://ifindv.github.io/posts/claude-code-08-checkpoints/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;检查点允许你保存对话状态并回溯到之前的点。这对于探索不同的方法、从错误中恢复或比较替代方案非常有用。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>claude code 教程：plugins</title><link>https://ifindv.github.io/posts/claude-code-07-plugins/</link><pubDate>Tue, 28 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://ifindv.github.io/posts/claude-code-07-plugins/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;插件是整合了command、subagent、MCP、hooks的高阶扩展机制。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>claude code 教程：hooks</title><link>https://ifindv.github.io/posts/claude-code-06-hooks/</link><pubDate>Mon, 27 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://ifindv.github.io/posts/claude-code-06-hooks/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;钩子是 claude code 会话里特定事件触发自动运行的脚本，可实现自动化、校验、权限管控、自定义工作流。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>claude code 教程：MCP</title><link>https://ifindv.github.io/posts/claude-code-05-mcp/</link><pubDate>Sun, 26 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://ifindv.github.io/posts/claude-code-05-mcp/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;MCP（Model Context Protocol）是claude访问外部工具、API和实时数据源的标准方式。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>claude code 教程：subagents</title><link>https://ifindv.github.io/posts/claude-code-04-subagents/</link><pubDate>Sat, 25 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://ifindv.github.io/posts/claude-code-04-subagents/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;子代理是claude code可委派任务的专业AI助手，具备独立上下文，可进行tools访问控制，定制系统提示词。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>claude code 教程：skills</title><link>https://ifindv.github.io/posts/claude-code-03-skills/</link><pubDate>Fri, 24 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://ifindv.github.io/posts/claude-code-03-skills/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;skills将领域知识、工作流程、最佳实践打包成可复用的组件。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>claude code教程：memory</title><link>https://ifindv.github.io/posts/claude-code-02-memory/</link><pubDate>Thu, 23 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://ifindv.github.io/posts/claude-code-02-memory/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;memory使claude具备context持久化与跨会话共享能力。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>claude code教程：commands</title><link>https://ifindv.github.io/posts/claude-code-01-commands/</link><pubDate>Wed, 22 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://ifindv.github.io/posts/claude-code-01-commands/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;commands提供了调用claude预定义能力的快捷方式。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>